    "body" : "In addition to what @C3roe stated: if you decide to treat everything as a regex, you can use the <code>\\Q</code> and <code>\\E</code> escape sequences or <code>Pattern.quote()</code> to convert a string literal to a regex. That would give you something like <code>private final String[] replies = { Pattern.quote(&quot;Step is done: 123,345&quot;), Pattern.quote(&quot;+OK&quot;), &quot;Process [0-9]+ finished&quot; };</code>"
